@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram - Search Users

[*] --> SearchUsers

state "Search users" as SearchUsers {
    [*] --> ChoiceProfile

    state ChoiceProfile <<choice>>
    state "View user profile" as ViewProfile
    state "Add to contacts" as AddToContacts

    ChoiceProfile --> ViewProfile : [view details]
    ChoiceProfile --> AddToContacts : [add contact]
}

SearchUsers : entry / Search users
SearchUsers : do / Search for users
SearchUsers : exit / After search results displayed

ViewProfile --> [*] : [Back to search]
AddToContacts --> [*] : [Back to search]
@enduml
